OL,3,CWoman given six months to live 'still
OL,4,Chere' seven years after medical trial
OL,6,FA woman who was given just six months
OL,7,Fto live after being diagnosed with two
OL,8,Fforms of has praised the medical trial
OL,9,Fthat she says has allowed her to live
OL,10,Ffor seven years since her diagnosis.
OL,12,FFarhana Badat, a former postmistress
OL,13,Ffrom , was first diagnosed with breast
OL,14,Fcancer in 2013, before being told it
OL,15,Fhad spread to her bones in 2016.
OL,17,FShe was initially told she may only
OL,18,Fhave six months to live as the type of
OL,19,Fcancer she had was no longer curable
OL,20,Fand had started to become resistant to
OL,21,Fhormone therapy.
