OL,3,CWoman given six months to live 'still
OL,4,Chere' seven years after medical trial
OL,6,FIt led to Farhanna taking part in a
OL,7,Ftrial called FAKTION through Velindre
OL,8,FCancer Centre in Cardiff in 2016.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru's Wales This
OL,11,FWeek programme, Farhana said: "When I
OL,12,Ffirst came, I only had six months to
OL,13,Flive and now I've had seven years
OL,14,Fsince then.
OL,16,F"I only had two grandchildren (then)
OL,17,Fand I now have six, so I've seen four
OL,18,Fborn.
