OL,4,Chere' seven years after medical trial
OL,6,F"We've had time together, we've done
OL,7,Fholidays together, places we wouldn't
OL,8,Fhave been if I'd been more ill.
OL,10,F"Wonderfully with all the help from
OL,11,FVelindre and God Allah, I'm still
OL,12,Fhere, still enjoying life."
OL,14,FPrior to taking part, patients are
OL,15,Ftold they could experience unexpected
OL,16,For serious side effects and the
OL,17,Fdecision whether to take part in a
OL,18,Ftrial or not rests with patients.
