OL,6,FKnowing there was a risk that an
OL,7,Fexperimental treatment could harm a
OL,8,Fpatient, Farhana's husband, Salim,
OL,9,Ftold Wales This Week the initial
OL,10,Fdecision was a difficult one.
OL,12,F"The doctor gave us an option,
OL,13,Fchemotherapy or a trial," he said.
OL,14,F"She (Farhanna) said 'I don't want
OL,15,Fchemotherapy'.
OL,17,F"I was shocked. I said 'think about
OL,18,Fit' and she said 'no I don't want
OL,19,Fchemotherapy'.
