OL,3,CWoman given six months to live 'still
OL,4,Chere' seven years after medical trial
OL,6,F"The beauty is the medicine they're
OL,7,Fgiving people now. I'm very proud of
OL,8,Fit, how it helps other people."
OL,10,FThe new drug involved in the trial is
OL,11,Fcalled Capivaertib, and it has been
OL,12,Fused alongside hormone therapy.
OL,14,FIt has now been approved by the Food
OL,15,Fand Drug Agency (FDA) in the United
OL,16,FStates, meaning it could be rolled out
OL,17,Fto other patients across the UK.
