OL,6,FProfessor Rob Jones, Early Phase
OL,7,FCancer Trials Lead in Wales, who is
OL,8,Falso a consultant at Velindre
OL,9,Foverseeing Farhana's treatment, said:
OL,10,F"The trial effectively showed that
OL,11,Fthere was a very significant
OL,12,Fimprovement in patient outcomes.
OL,14,F"When I'm talking about that it's
OL,15,Fabout how long a patient's cancer is
OL,16,Fcontrolled for and how long patients
OL,17,Flive for.
