OL,3,CWoman given six months to live 'still
OL,4,Chere' seven years after medical trial
OL,6,F"By adding a new drug into standard
OL,7,Fhormone treatment, and combining it
OL,8,Fwith hormone therapy, we found that
OL,9,Fpatients could live twice as long when
OL,10,Fcompared to patients who had hormone
OL,11,Ftherapy and a placebo."
OL,13,FThe approval by the FDA means the drug
OL,14,Fcan now go through the UK's National
OL,15,FInstitute for Health and Care
OL,16,FExcellence (NICE).
OL,18,FNICE may then recommend the drug be
OL,19,Fused to treat patients within the NHS.
