OL,6,FWhile clinicians and patients wait to
OL,7,Ffind out if the drug and treatment
OL,8,Fwill be rolled out, Farhana will
OL,9,Fcontinue to receive the treatment.
OL,11,F"(Taking part in the trial) is my only
OL,12,Fway of giving back at the moment," she
OL,13,Fcontinued.
OL,15,F"I feel like if you even help one
OL,16,Fperson and if they get as much fun and
OL,17,Fjoy out of life then it's worth it in
OL,18,Fthe end.
